'''''Secrets of the Dark Side''''' was the holy book of the [[Church of the Dark Side]] and one of the central cruxes of the [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] hoax that was the Church. The book, collected by the false [[Heingort Giddis|Jedgar]], contained the "prophecies" of the false [[Rajah Ubooki|Kadann]].

[[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Peccati Syn]] lent his fellow Grand Admiral, [[Ishin-Il-Raz]], his personal ''Secrets of the Dark Side'' after the latter grew depressed following the death of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].

